IEEE cases¶

Case 4gs¶

pandapower.networks.case4gs()¶

Calls the pickle file case4gs.p which data origin is pypower.

RETURN:

net - Returns the required ieee network case4gs

EXAMPLE:

import pandapower.networks as pn

net = pn.case4gs()
